✨Buenos dias✨ just a little reintroduction to who I am and what ¡Looking Bilingüe! is all about! 🌎🎶

My work combines theatre, movement and song to teach ESL and Heritage Spanish to kids, I also lead Heritage Latiné empowerment groups and an interview series for adults. Inspired by my toddler and the power of culture, I'm reintroducing my teaching artistry and taking it to new heights! ☀️

Whether you're part of the Latino Community or an ally let's celebrate culture through the arts together! 🌎🎉

Is reconnecting with our roots, empowering Latinos and their families who feel ni de aquí ni de allá! 🌎 We're bringing language to life through theater, song, and movement for kiddos in schools, and creating safe spaces with Community sharing circles for adults. ✨ Stay tuned for more storytelling, Latiné empowerment, and so much more! 🎉 Reach out for details -- exciting things are coming your way!
